IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SELECTION-SORT.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  ARR-SIZE     PIC 9(2) VALUE 5.
01  ARR          PIC 9(3) OCCURS 5 TIMES.
01  I            PIC 9(2).
01  J            PIC 9(2).
01  MIN-INDEX    PIC 9(2).
01  TEMP         PIC 9(3).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 034 TO ARR(1).
    MOVE 012 TO ARR(2).
    MOVE 045 TO ARR(3).
    MOVE 023 TO ARR(4).
    MOVE 009 TO ARR(5).

    PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I = ARR-SIZE
        MOVE I TO MIN-INDEX
        PERFORM VARYING J FROM I + 1 BY 1 UNTIL J > ARR-SIZE
            IF ARR(J) < ARR(MIN-INDEX) THEN
                MOVE J TO MIN-INDEX
            END-IF
        END-PERFORM
        IF MIN-INDEX NOT = I THEN
            MOVE ARR(I) TO TEMP
            MOVE ARR(MIN-INDEX) TO ARR(I)
            MOVE TEMP TO ARR(MIN-INDEX)
        END-IF
    END-PERFORM.

    DISPLAY "ARRAY ORDENADO:".
    PERFORM VARYING I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL I > ARR-SIZE
        DISPLAY ARR(I)
    END-PERFORM.

    STOP RUN.
